name: Big bird in a small cage
description:
The woman in a picture is wearing a wedding dress. She has a wings. She can fly anywhere to the place she would love to. There is no cage in picture because sometimes the thing we call 'a cage' has not always be seen. The dark planet behind her back is represented the world she's livin' in the background: Mars. A symbol of men's planet.

It's a criticize of patriarchy system in our society.
